@node Main "Midnight Blanker Document"

  The fish of Midnight are happy as long as they get lots of fish

  food.  It might not be easy for these guys.  Boy are they large

  or what?  Ok, so maybe they don't eat fish food, and maybe they

  still need to be "oiled", but they have young fish class.


